strings: <voice_0x01001772><se_def>*: Which is not important. we are still dying

<voice_0x01001776><se_low>jungmi: Will Dragovia make it?Things are worse than they appear.
<voice_0x01001777><se_low>jungmi: You should get to know other parents. Please, fix it!
